channel.title: Regicide Development
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i42.tinypic.com/13zzvdk.png[/img][/center]
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/DHXUh.png[/img]
Welcome all to my Regicide Development Thread. Here I will be posting updates/ and releases for my new project "Regicide" I got the name from a recent Project that did not actually work from another person. This project will be 100% and I will not quit on you guy's. I am planning on releasing this sometime soon whenever I can make this the best it can be.[/center] [center][b] Information[/b]
Regicide is a 317 Project Insanity server. It has 562 Gameframe, and you can pick between the lower gameframes from 562 to pick from in-game. It has donator benefits, and all bosses are working. Once I am done coding with this server, and putting it all together I can guarantee this server will be 100% awesomeness. If you have any questions please message me on skype, or read below to contacting me. [/center]
[center][b]Regicide Team[/b]
- [img]http://rs2gold.net/sitey/content/img/layout/icons/crown_gold.gif[/img]Barrick/ Owner & Programmer - Open - Open - Open
All spot's that are open are below, if you are interested in joining please keep reading further[/center]
[center][b]Joining the Team/Spots[/b]
- Needed Coder/Programmer - Needed Forum Developer - Needed Forum & In-Game Moderator[/center]
[center][b]Regicide Team Application[/b]
[code]Skype/MSN: Experience: What Spot: Link to Your Work: Name: Will You Stay With Us: Other Information:[/code]
Please post this below in a quote to this Thread.[/center]
[center] [img]http://i.imgur.com/gYrH3.png[/img]
Media Coming Soon...[/center]
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/RVzsD.png[/img]
[code]Fixed Bank Interface New Home Added More Ranks In-Game Removed all Dupes/Bugs 100% Slayer Rewritten [/code]
I have not done much, since I have been busy, but now I am ready.[/center]
[center][b]Contacting Me![/b]
- Skype/ Burrickz - MSN/ Leonidous@live.com
If you added me on either one, please inform me.
